summary: I created this mod as a joke between friends, I quite liked the quest complete audio from Witcher 3, So I replaced the Skyrim Level Up Audio with it.
descriptionHtml:
[center]
[size=3]This simple audio replacer takes the sound that plays when a quest is completed in the Witcher 3 and replaces the Skyrim level up audio with it.

[/size][size=3]Always wished you could have a random woman scream at you when leveling your character? Wish no more.

Install Via your preferred mod organizer and start the game as normal. [/size][/center]
author: Stiptikspec
